sequenceDiagram
    participant Main as UIMainUICtrl
    participant Map as MainMap
    participant Item as GKItem
    participant Net as HttpManager
    participant UI as UIController/UIManager
    participant Game as UIGameUICtrl

    Main->>Map: loadTableView(realHeight)
    Note right of Map: 预热GK缓存、构建长列表、定位到当前关卡

    Main->>Main: 点击“开始” 或 关卡选择
    Main->>Net: Play/PlayTest(id = 当前关卡)
    Net-->>Main: PlayResponse(map/plan/limits)

    Main->>UI: Destroy UIMain
    Main->>UI: emit uiGame({gameType: Normal})
    UI-->>Game: 创建 UIGameUICtrl 及子系统

